arCallbacks.szOnCallbackCompleteScript:
function Start()
	
	idOrinaClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(idActorOrina, true)
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idOrinaClone) then
    	Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idOrinaClone, false)
    	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idOrinaClone, locTowerExit, "NPC_WALK", true)
		Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(idOrinaClone, 0.3)
	end
	if (Hydra.QuestIsRestoredFromSave(false)) then
		Hydra.EventSendToActor("OrinaLeaves", idSelf, idSelf)
	end
end

function Start()

	--Completing the Conversation Finished prevents the Quest Pin from reappearing on the NPC while the flippy is out.
	Hydra.QuestCallbackSetComplete(106)

end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	Hydra.QuestCallbackSetComplete(106)
	
	idQuestOwner = Hydra.QuestGetOwner()

	Hydra.ItemGiveQuestItemToPlayer(idQuestOwner, "QST_Hawe_Verge_Taissa_01_Item_RitualSupplies", "QST_Hawe_Verge_Taissa_01")
end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)

	idTaissaClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(idTaissaOutside)
	
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idTaissaClone, idTaissaWalkLoc, "NPC_Walk", false)
	Hydra.QActorDeleteNPCClone(idTaissaClone, 0.5)
	
end
